chhodenge na ham tera saath o saathi marte dam tak
marte dam tak nahi agle janam tak
agle janam nahi saat janam tak
saat janam nahi janam janam tak
chhodenge na hamteri hi tasveer saji hai dil ke aaine mein
tujhse mohabbat kar ke lajjat pa hi gaye jeene mein
deta hai khushiyaan ab tera gam tak
padne na denge gam ke kadam tak
kadam rakhenge sang janam janam tak
chhodenge na hamkoi dhunde apne ko koi apne sanam ko
apna khuda bhi apna sanam bhi mil gaya tujhse hamko
kar liye vaade khaai kasam tak
khaai kasam dil ke sangam tak
sangam hoga janam janam tak
chhodenge na hammausam aate jaate rahenge saavan phaagun laate rahenge
pyaar bhare dil pyaar ke nagamein
is mausam se us mausam tak
is aalam se us aalam tak
duur na honge janam janam tak
chhodenge na ham